cs.AR, cs.ET, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.CV 

The paper proposes multiplierless algorithms and computational architectures for 4 × 4 approximate-discrete cosine transform (DCT) for transform coding in digital video. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 

- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture)
- cs.ET (Embedded Systems)
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms)
- cs.IT (Information Theory)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
